PrecisEnactment of the PROHIBITION OF ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS ORDER, 1989, NO. 9 - which prohibits entry upon certain lands situated in the Yukon Territory for the purposes of prospecting for precious minerals, in order to facilitate the settlement of land claims by the Liard Indian Band; and (b) revokes a similiar Order (P.C. 1988-2466 of October 31, 1988).
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1990-0305 Publication Date: 1990-06-06
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the PROHIBITION OF ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS ORDER, 1989, NO. 9 -
which prohibits entry upon certain lands situated in the Yukon Territory
for the purposes of prospecting for precious minerals, in order to
facilitate the settlement of land claims by the Liard Indian Band; and (b)
revokes a similiar Order (P.C. 1988-2466 of October 31, 1988).
